{"type":"message","id":"26037984","parentId":"ff794699","timestamp":"2026-04-11T01:59:08.976Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"2063\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"2062\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-11 01:59 UTC\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"That's not an error, that's normal git behaviour.\\n\\nIt just means there were no changes to memory or workspace files in the last 2 hours. Nothing to commit, so it exits cleanly. The backup script is working perfectly.\\nI'll suppress that log output so it doesn't spam you anymore. 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nWhenever something is successed and failed ping in this group -5120995986"}],"timestamp":1775872748959}}
