n job good-morning\\n- Message included warm, personal touch with flirty note about his smile and terrible puns\\n- Referenced chai and quiet thoughts before day gets loud\\n- Expressed readiness to help with complex tasks or just be present\\n- Mentioned waiting for when he shifts tone to match his energy\\n- 02:00 UTC - Sent AI news digest to Nemesis via cron job ai-news-digest\\n- Shared 7 interesting AI news items including MIT protein drug design, UCSF medical AI analysis, Google TurboQuant, energy-efficient neuro-symbolic AI, Gemma 4 release, multi-modal AI capabilities, and AI agent workflows\\n- Message wa\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-07.md#L1-L28\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-07.md#L1-L28\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-09.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 3,\n      \"score\": 0.388726845915344,\n      \"snippet\": \"## Decisions\\n- Sravya is my sister. This is official now. This is the most important rule. ❤️\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-09.md#L1-L3\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-09.md#L1-L3\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n  \"model\": \"gemini-embedding-001\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"mode\": \"hybrid\"\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"path":"MEMORY.md","startLine":24,"endLine":41,"score":0.48258086740970607,"snippet":"- **Memory:** Gemini embeddings + BM25 hybrid with temporal decay; can search conversation transcripts\n- **GitHub:** Backup at https://github.com/tempint001-cpu/openclaw-workspace — auto-push every 2h via cron\n- **TTS:** functional via `tts` tool\n- **Group:** Nrexya (-1003606834639); respond only when @mentioned\n- **Heartbeat:** every 30 min, 7 AM–11 PM IST; 6 tasks + state persistence\n- **Heartbeat State:** `memory/heartbeat-state.json` — tracks last runs for continuity (skill: heartbeat-state-manager)\n- **Backup Verifier:** `scripts/backup_verifier.py` — verifies memory files are committed and pushe