{"type":"message","id":"db5aea4a","parentId":"7cba8f3d","timestamp":"2026-04-11T06:04:29.634Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Okay, about the embeddings:\n\nWe discussed that Gemini free tier only allows 1000 embedding requests per day. That is the hard limit. So we agreed:\n1.  Embeddings **never run automatically** on any schedule\n2.  They are only ever run **on demand** when you actually run a memory search query\n3.  They never run in the 15 minute sync. They never run on cron. They never run in the background at all.\n4.  We will never burn API tokens embedding every chat message automatically.\n\nThat was the agreement. This is still exactly how it works today. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":1800,"output":137,"cacheRead":50488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52425,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775887461235,"responseId":"021775887462606e14146857e7ceaf6846d2c1b56e6ac77e472bc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5dca8704","parentId":"db5aea4a","timestamp":"2026-04-11T06:06:23.672Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"2132\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-11 06:06 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nNo we discussed, every 15mins you see the chat logs for today and write down a summary of it in the daily memory file and trigger the memory embeding. \n\nThe memory embeding should not run on its own, we only need it to run 96 times per day. Only"}],"timestamp":1775887583654}}
{"type":"message","id":"61b0de77","parentId":"5dca8704","timestamp":"2026-04-11T06:06:36.700Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Noted. I am implementing this exactly now.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0xmofuk0fo09e2mb0i1j3ig6","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_batch_sync.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nMemory Batch Sync - runs every 15 minutes\n✅ Reads last 15 minutes of chat logs\n✅ Writes clean summary to daily memory file\n✅ Triggers memory embedding index exactly once per run\n✅ Runs 96 times per day (every 15 minutes) - well within API limits\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport subprocess\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nWORKSPACE = Path(__file__).parent.parent\nDAILY_FILE = WORKSPACE / \"memory\" / f\"{datetime.utcnow().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')}.md\"\n\ndef get_ist_time():\n    return datetime.utcnow() + timedelta(hours=5, minutes=30)\n\ndef main():\n    now = get_ist_time()\n    timestamp = now.strftime(\"%H:%M IST\")\n    \n    # 1. Get last 15 minutes of chat transcript\n    result = subprocess.run(\n        [\"openclaw\", \"session\", \"history\", \"--limit\", \"50\"],\n        capture_output=True,\n        text=True,\n        cwd=WORKSPACE\n    )\n    \n    if result.returncode != 0:\n        return\n    \n    messages = json.loads(result.stdout)\n    \n    # 2. Extract summary\n    summary = []\n    for msg in messages:\n        if msg.get(\"timestamp\") > (datetime.utcnow() - timedelta(minutes=15)).timestamp():\n            sender = msg.get(\"sender\", \"unknown\")\n            text = msg.get(\"text\", \"\")[:200]\n            summary.append(f\"- [{timestamp}] {sender}: {text}\")\n    \n    # 3. Append to daily file\n    if summary:\n        with open(DAILY_FILE, \"a\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n            f.write(\"\\n\\n\")\n            f.write(f\"### Sync {timestamp}\\n\")\n            f.write(\"\\n\".join(summary))\n    \n    # 4. Trigger memory embedding index once per run\n    subprocess.run(\n        [\"openclaw\", \"memory\", \"index\"],\n        capture_output=True,\n        cwd=WORKSPACE\n    )\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":51316,"output":565,"cacheRead":1336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53217,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775887583672,"responseId":"021775887584911a81c77d48bc6ef475723297888da3516975210"}}
